com.gotenna.sdk.responses

Class SystemInfoResponseData

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.gotenna.sdk.responses.SystemInfoResponseData

  • public class SystemInfoResponseData
extends java.lang.Object
    A model representing the info sent back to us by the goTenna. Contains helpful info such as the current battery level and firmware version of the goTenna. Created on 4/10/15.
